    "Finally, a two-level matching model is proposed for accurately and efficiently matching the spatial relation graph.",
    "Dai et al. (2022) proposed a new place recognition method named SC-LPR, which uses spatiotemporal contextual information from LiDAR scans to increase the capacity of feature representation.",
